1
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:13,340
Eternal Love of Dream

2
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:23,660
Episode 53

3
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:30,460
Well,

4
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:33,260
do these spiritual birds

5
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:34,420
fly here to dance every year?

6
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,420
Do you think they've got nothing else to do?

7
00:02:43,180 --> 00:02:45,020
So you summoned them specially?

8
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:45,740
Well,

9
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:46,700
well,

10
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:48,660
just ask them to come closer.

11
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:50,740
Ask them to do the dance of
"Paying Homage to the Phoenix" for me closer.

12
00:02:57,940 --> 00:03:00,340
I won't do it for nothing.

13
00:03:01,380 --> 00:03:02,580
How will you return the favor?

14
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:05,860
Don't be so stingy.

15
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:08,460
I've taught you how to make the sweet and sour fish.

16
00:03:11,060 --> 00:03:12,660
Or do you want to watch me dance?

17
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:14,980
I'm quite a good dancer,

18
00:03:15,260 --> 00:03:16,180
far better than

19
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,580
your foster sister Zhihe.

20
00:03:18,220 --> 00:03:20,260
I just can't dance for others.

21
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:23,580
Just make them do the dance of

22
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:24,340
"Paying Homage to the Phoenix" for me.

23
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:24,980
Never in my life

24
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:25,780
have I watched real birds

25
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:27,780
do the dance of "Paying Homage to the Phoenix".

26
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:29,180
If you ask them to dance for me,

27
00:03:29,220 --> 00:03:30,580
I'll dance for you.

28
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:31,860
Xiaobai,

29
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:35,180
in front of others,

30
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:36,380
you're always polite and well-behaved,

31
00:03:37,540 --> 00:03:39,260
pretending to be elegant and experienced,

32
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:41,100
but I know that you're just

33
00:03:41,100 --> 00:03:43,020
a mischievous and spoiled girl.

34
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:46,900
You used to restrain yourself in front of me,

35
00:03:47,140 --> 00:03:48,380
for example, in the Fanyin Valley

36
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:50,700
and in the Dream of Aranya.

37
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:54,140
Compared to the previous girl
who was restrained in front of me,

38
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:56,500
I like the present girl more,

39
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:58,380
who is innocent and spoiled.

40
00:03:58,740 --> 00:03:59,860
This is the real you.

41
00:04:01,180 --> 00:04:02,540
Miao Luo once said that

42
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:03,940
there was a sea of Foling flowers in my heart.

43
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:06,740
She wondered who was hidden behind the flowers.

44
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:08,140
Xiaobai,

45
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:10,900
I know that there has always been

46
00:04:11,460 --> 00:04:13,420
a little red fox hiding behind the flowers.

47
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:16,660
Though I was not in love with you back then,

48
00:04:16,900 --> 00:04:20,140
I've always treated you differently.

49
00:04:20,340 --> 00:04:22,660
Just make them dance for me.

50
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:23,900
Don't ignore me.

51
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:25,940
It's a real bargain!

52
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:31,780
It really is!

53
00:04:33,180 --> 00:04:36,340
Then you should dance for me first.

54
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:38,100
Well,

55
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:40,780
we'd better not keep
the spiritual birds waiting for too long.

56
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:43,020
Can you ask them to dance for me first?

57
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,380
I'll dance for you later.

58
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:46,180
As a majestic god,

59
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:47,900
you should show compassion.

60
00:04:49,340 --> 00:04:51,860
I'm just afraid that someone might act in a slick way.

61
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:53,660
Didn't you say

62
00:04:54,420 --> 00:04:57,020
you really wanted to return the favor?

63
00:04:58,340 --> 00:04:59,740
Now you're bargaining with me.

64
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:04,340
Where's your sincerity?

65
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:14,820
Since there's no music,

66
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:16,420
I can only do one part of the dance.

67
00:05:17,060 --> 00:05:18,100
Now that you're dancing,

68
00:05:18,700 --> 00:05:20,380
you should do the whole dance at least.

69
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:23,980
I'll play the music for you.

70
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:31,300
You actually know how to play Konghou!

71
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:34,020
I didn't know that.

72
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,380
I didn't play much.

73
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:37,620
Of course you didn't know.

74
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:42,580
Do you find your husband talented?

75
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:43,940
Hu...

76
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:44,660
Hus...

77
00:05:45,420 --> 00:05:46,100
Husband.

78
00:05:46,780 --> 00:05:49,580
It's weird to hear you say that.

79
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:52,020
No!

80
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:54,420
The word "husband" is weird itself.

81
00:05:54,660 --> 00:05:56,300
I'd better keep calling you "Your Majesty".

82
00:05:58,700 --> 00:05:59,540
Come here.

83
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:09,180
What did you just call me?

84
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:11,260
Think it clearly.

85
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:14,180
I called you "Your Majesty".

86
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,300
Who am I to you?

87
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:19,780
Husband! You're my husband!

88
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:22,300
That's more like it.

89
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:25,620
Dance for me over there.

90
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:34,260
You said you wanted to dance for me,

91
00:06:34,860 --> 00:06:37,220
but you haven't started yet.

92
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:40,940
Don't you find yourself hard to deal with?

93
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:43,660
You're the one who's been messing with me!

94
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:03,420
Xiaobai,

95
00:07:04,940 --> 00:07:06,940
I've always known that you're pretty,

96
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:09,500
but you're not the enchanting type

97
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:13,340
for you often bear an innocent and bright look.

98
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:16,420
How ridiculous I am! Only till now

99
00:07:17,420 --> 00:07:19,060
do I realize that this innocent face

100
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:22,460
is actually coquettish.

101
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:26,500
Look at those gentle and soft eyes!

102
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:28,900
Are you trying to seduce me?

103
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:48,580
Come to me.

104
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:51,380
One minute you asked me to come here,

105
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:52,660
and the next minute, you asked me to come to you.

106
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:54,140
You should come to me yourself.

107
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,860
Why do you bother me all the time?

108
00:07:57,900 --> 00:07:58,780
Please come to me!

109
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:08,060
Then you can't pet me.

110
00:08:10,100 --> 00:08:10,980
I won't.

111
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,340
Really?

112
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:15,100
Yes.

113
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:23,740
I...

114
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:26,660
I still have to watch the dance of
"Paying Homage to the Phoenix".

115
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:29,500
What's the fun in that?

116
00:08:30,860 --> 00:08:32,220
Just watch me instead.

117
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:57,100
As long as Dong Hua doesn't investigate himself,

118
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:58,700
no one else can see through

119
00:08:58,700 --> 00:09:00,340
my hallucinating ward.

120
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,180
What if Emperor Dong Hua comes here?

121
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:06,060
Then let's do it on his wedding day.

122
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:08,620
Even if anything happens to the demons,

123
00:09:08,860 --> 00:09:10,300
he won't be able to come.

124
00:09:11,540 --> 00:09:12,500
Yes!

125
00:09:14,420 --> 00:09:15,860
Nie Chuyin,

126
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:19,540
I have limited patience.

127
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:22,100
If anything goes wrong again...

128
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:23,420
Your Majesty, do feel relieved.

129
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:27,020
If I can't get the blood tear this time,

130
00:09:27,380 --> 00:09:28,940
I'll end my life myself.

131
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:35,500
Don't move!

132
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:37,460
Your body was just made.

133
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:39,180
You need rest.

134
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:46,620
It's time!

135
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:57,380
I thought the delayed wedding banquet

136
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:59,540
is just an ordinary banquet,

137
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:01,540
so I only have to dress formally.

138
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:03,660
I didn't expect to dress so fancily.

139
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:09,220
It's just like a dream!

140
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:14,460
Xiaobai,

141
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:18,820
I'll have this dream with you forever.

142
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:26,900
Your Majesty! Your Highness!

143
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:31,700
I didn't mean to interrupt.

144
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:33,740
I really have something urgent to report.

145
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:34,660
Never mind.

146
00:10:36,860 --> 00:10:37,500
What's up?

147
00:10:38,940 --> 00:10:40,660
Has anything gone wrong with Ye Qingti?

148
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:42,300
Your Highness, please don't worry.

149
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:43,460
The time has come.

150
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:44,980
Ye Qingti is about to wake up.

151
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:47,140
It's time to transfer cultivation to him.

152
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:49,340
Really?

153
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:51,060
I just

154
00:10:51,380 --> 00:10:52,780
confirmed that.

155
00:10:53,260 --> 00:10:54,420
Wonderful!

156
00:10:55,420 --> 00:10:56,260
Your Highness, I know that

157
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:58,660
you've been worried about Ye Qingti all the time,

158
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:00,380
so I came here to inform you.

159
00:11:00,820 --> 00:11:01,700
Thank you, Lord Xie.

160
00:11:02,020 --> 00:11:03,420
Your Highness, you're welcome.

161
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:05,660
The earlier Ye Qingti obtains cultivation,

162
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:07,820
the earlier he can start cultivating.

163
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:08,940
Thus, he can wash away the mortal dust

164
00:11:09,140 --> 00:11:10,780
in the Ninth Heaven Jade Pool

165
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:12,180
and become an immortal earlier in future.

166
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:15,300
Well then, I'll go right away.

167
00:11:19,180 --> 00:11:20,380
Transfer cultivation to him?

168
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:23,940
Are you going to do that yourself?

169
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:26,540
He died because of me.

170
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:28,980
I can at least do this for him.

171
00:11:30,620 --> 00:11:31,140
No.

172
00:11:34,340 --> 00:11:36,300
Sorry for breaking into the hall without reporting.

173
00:11:37,140 --> 00:11:38,700
I should go and do some repair work

174
00:11:38,940 --> 00:11:39,860
on Ye Qingti's body
so as to reduce possible problems he might have

175
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:42,180
when he becomes an immortal in future.

176
00:11:43,380 --> 00:11:44,940
Your Majesty! Your Highness!

177
00:11:45,180 --> 00:11:46,900
I'm leaving.

178
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:53,980
Ye Qingti saved my life.

179
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:55,780
If I don't transfer my cultivation to him,

180
00:11:56,060 --> 00:11:57,900
who will?

181
00:11:58,740 --> 00:11:59,220
Xiaobai,

182
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:01,700
having given Ye Qingti an immortal body,

183
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:05,340
you've paid back his favor.

184
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:08,220
