185
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:16,780
Your Majesty,

186
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:19,660
are you so in love with me that

187
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:22,820
you can't bear to hear that I'm going to

188
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:24,740
transfer my cultivation to another man?

189
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:29,460
You're just a little fox over thirty thousand years old.

190
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:31,140
You don't have much cultivation.

191
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:33,220
If you give away half of your cultivation,

192
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:35,540
how can you survive the test and become a superior goddess

193
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:39,060
if I'm not by your side in the future?

194
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:42,940
So it's only because of my poor cultivation.

195
00:12:45,700 --> 00:12:46,380
Moreover,

196
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:48,380
even if I have to go through the test
of becoming a superior goddess,

197
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:50,580
that'll be tens of thousands of years later.

198
00:12:50,900 --> 00:12:51,900
You just said

199
00:12:52,060 --> 00:12:53,820
you wanted to be with me forever.

200
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:56,580
How can you not be with me then?

201
00:12:59,180 --> 00:12:59,860
Right.

202
00:13:01,060 --> 00:13:03,100
I'll definitely be with you.

203
00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:06,860
Such being the case,

204
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:08,420
let me transfer

205
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:11,420
my cultivation to him.

206
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:12,940
Your Majesty,

207
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:14,380
how can I let you

208
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:15,620
transfer your cultivation to him?

209
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:16,740
Everything you do is concerned with

210
00:13:16,940 --> 00:13:18,900
the stability of the Four Seas and Eight Deserts.

211
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:21,420
You'll have to give away half of your cultivation,

212
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:22,660
but I only have to give

213
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:24,420
a tiny bit of my cultivation.

214
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:25,620
I won't be affected.

215
00:13:26,060 --> 00:13:26,620
No! No!

216
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:27,740
Your Majesty,

217
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:29,460
I know you're saying this for my good,

218
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:31,660
but Ye Qingti saved my life.

219
00:13:31,980 --> 00:13:33,580
Though I can't respond to his love,

220
00:13:33,780 --> 00:13:35,180
I can definitely bring him back to life.

221
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:36,900
That's my promise to him.

222
00:13:37,420 --> 00:13:40,220
If I let Your Majesty fulfill my duties

223
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,140
all the time,

224
00:13:41,380 --> 00:13:42,780
how can my subjects

225
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:44,460
trust me in future?

226
00:13:45,620 --> 00:13:46,100
Xiaobai...

227
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:47,500
Your Majesty,

228
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:49,740
I'm the Monarch of Qingqiu.

229
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:52,940
I'm not a woman

230
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:54,780
who needs your protection all the time.

231
00:13:57,860 --> 00:13:58,500
I know.

232
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:00,820
You've always been strong and independent.

233
00:14:01,940 --> 00:14:04,460
I'm the one who can't live without you.

234
00:14:10,220 --> 00:14:12,100
Then I'll go with you

235
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:14,500
after our wedding.

236
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:17,820
Let's go together then.

