00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:07,940
the wedding etiquette

283
00:18:08,180 --> 00:18:09,580
is merely a formality.

284
00:18:09,900 --> 00:18:10,500
His Majesty said

285
00:18:10,740 --> 00:18:11,700
he wouldn't restrain me.

286
00:18:12,060 --> 00:18:13,940
I can do whatever I like.

287
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:18,060
Did His Majesty really say so?

288
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:19,300
Of course!

289
00:18:23,180 --> 00:18:24,380
He has kept his words.

290
00:18:24,980 --> 00:18:26,940
However, even so,

291
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:29,460
the Sky Kingdom is not Qingqiu.

292
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:32,260
You should be prudent and self-restraint in future.

293
00:18:32,700 --> 00:18:34,860
Don't be willful as you were in Qingqiu.

294
00:18:35,060 --> 00:18:35,980
Do you understand?

295
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:37,700
I see.

296
00:18:38,020 --> 00:18:39,900
If there's any rule I don't understand in the Sky Kingdom,

297
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:41,660
I'll consult Immortal Officials such as Chong Lin.

298
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:42,740
Father, do feel relieved.

299
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,580
Well. Father, I'm leaving.

300
00:18:45,820 --> 00:18:46,940
Mother has got plenty of things

301
00:18:47,140 --> 00:18:47,980
for me to handle.

302
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:49,660
Are you really so anxious?

303
00:18:55,020 --> 00:18:56,220
Father, what's wrong?

304
00:19:01,820 --> 00:19:04,860
Xiaojiu, you've grown up.

305
00:19:05,570 --> 00:19:07,380
You're about to become the Empress.

306
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:09,460
Father,

307
00:19:09,780 --> 00:19:11,460
I'm just getting married.

308
00:19:11,820 --> 00:19:12,500
Also,

309
00:19:12,740 --> 00:19:15,100
I'll often come back to visit you and mother.

310
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:16,300
Moreover,

311
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:18,220
His Majesty can practice the cloud-riding trick.

312
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:19,820
We can come to Qingqiu from the Sky Kingdom

313
00:19:19,820 --> 00:19:21,540
in a blink of an eye.

314
00:19:21,900 --> 00:19:24,820
Father, no need to be so sad.

315
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:26,420
You are going to

316
00:19:26,660 --> 00:19:29,420
become the Monarch and the Empress,

317
00:19:29,780 --> 00:19:31,100
but you're still so childish.

318
00:19:31,620 --> 00:19:33,220
Even if I'm going to become the Monarch and the Empress,

319
00:19:33,420 --> 00:19:35,060
I'm still your daughter.

320
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:38,100
In future,

321
00:19:38,460 --> 00:19:40,300
if His Majesty dares betray you...

322
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:43,980
Father, His Majesty really treats me well.

323
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:45,420
Do feel relieved.

324
00:19:45,620 --> 00:19:47,220
I'll be happy.

325
00:20:02,180 --> 00:20:03,180
She said she must see you,

326
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:05,980
and she asked me to bring this to you.

327
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:08,140
She said you would see her after seeing it.

328
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:51,780
Master, you've come at last.

329
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:58,140
This is left by your father.

330
00:20:58,660 --> 00:20:59,580
Put it away.

331
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:07,860
My father never asked you for any favor when he was alive.

332
00:21:08,940 --> 00:21:09,940
Master,

333
00:21:11,260 --> 00:21:13,580
this is the place where my father died.

334
00:21:13,980 --> 00:21:14,540
I...

335
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,820
I want to beg you

336
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:19,100
for another chance.

337
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:23,900
Even if...

338
00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:25,780
Even if I have to be a fairy maid

339
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:29,540
in your mansion for the rest of my life,

340
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:30,660
I'm fine with that.

341
00:21:32,460 --> 00:21:35,580
Master, for my father's sake,

342
00:21:35,940 --> 00:21:37,260
please have mercy on me

343
00:21:37,780 --> 00:21:39,460
and let me stay by your side.

344
00:21:40,300 --> 00:21:41,620
Before your father died,

345
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:43,180
he entrusted you to my care.

346
00:21:43,980 --> 00:21:44,780
However,

347
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:47,340
I never like to take care of

348
00:21:47,540 --> 00:21:49,620
someone who fancies me.

349
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:55,300
Fine.

350
00:21:58,980 --> 00:22:02,820
Now with this scale,

351
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:08,660
I want you to fulfill your promise to my father.

352
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:14,300
I want you to return my father's favor to me.

353
00:22:14,980 --> 00:22:16,780
I want you to divorce your wife,

354
00:22:18,700 --> 00:22:21,060
appoint no Empress,

355
00:22:22,900 --> 00:22:24,980
and never get married the rest of your life.

356
00:22:28,060 --> 00:22:29,820
Your father would never expect that

357
00:22:30,220 --> 00:22:33,340
you would use the promise this way.

358
00:23:15,700 --> 00:23:16,700
What time is it now?

359
00:23:17,620 --> 00:23:19,980
It'll be the auspicious moment in one hour.

360
00:23:22,980 --> 00:23:24,340
Fetch the ritual scroll for me.

361
00:23:24,620 --> 00:23:25,420
I'm gonna review it again.

362
00:23:25,860 --> 00:23:26,420
Yes.

363
00:23:34,820 --> 00:23:35,300
Your Highness!

364
00:23:36,340 --> 00:23:36,820
Chong Lin,

365
00:23:37,220 --> 00:23:38,460
where is His Majesty?

366
00:23:39,460 --> 00:23:40,220
I've no idea.

367
00:23:40,700 --> 00:23:41,900
But no need to worry.

368
00:23:42,340 --> 00:23:44,980
I suppose His Majesty is delayed by something urgent.

369
00:23:47,820 --> 00:23:48,860
Pardon me for being outspoken.

370
00:23:49,220 --> 00:23:51,140
If His Majesty can't get back on time today,

371
00:23:51,540 --> 00:23:52,780
we can turn today's wedding banquet into

372
00:23:52,940 --> 00:23:55,220
a normal celebration banquet.

373
00:23:57,620 --> 00:23:59,220
Actually, it's OK with me,

374
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:02,100
but my father and mother are here today.

375
00:24:02,340 --> 00:24:03,540
They've prepared for days

376
00:24:04,060 --> 00:24:05,340
so as to make this banquet

377
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:07,140
a real wedding banquet.

378
00:24:07,620 --> 00:24:09,300
If His Majesty doesn't show up,

379
00:24:09,780 --> 00:24:11,300
I'm afraid they may feel hurt.

380
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:14,940
Your Highness, when sending out invitations,

381
00:24:15,260 --> 00:24:16,300
we made it clear that

382
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:17,900
this would be a delayed wedding banquet.

383
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:20,300
As to what a delayed wedding banquet would be like,

384
00:24:20,620 --> 00:24:22,020
no one knows actually.

385
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:24,060
If we turn it into a normal celebration banquet

386
00:24:24,260 --> 00:24:26,740
for immortals to drink wine
and get together on this happy occasion,

387
00:24:27,260 --> 00:24:28,540
it won't seem odd.

388
00:24:28,940 --> 00:24:31,540
Nor will it embarrass your family from Qingqiu.

389
00:24:34,540 --> 00:24:36,140
This is actually a good idea.

390
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:40,540
His Majesty never likes banquet occasions.

391
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:41,980
He wouldn't show up

392
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:43,300
even for his own victory banquet.

393
00:24:43,580 --> 00:24:44,700
In case he doesn't show up today,

394
00:24:45,060 --> 00:24:46,660
it won't lead to any misunderstanding.

395
00:24:47,020 --> 00:24:47,580
Chong Lin,

396
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:49,460
I really appreciate that

397
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:50,700
you've considered these for me.

398
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:52,540
Your Highness,

399
00:24:53,620 --> 00:24:55,380
His Majesty takes the wedding banquet seriously.

400
00:24:55,780 --> 00:24:57,140
If he can't come back on time today,

401
00:24:57,220 --> 00:24:58,700
he must have encountered something urgent.

402
00:24:59,420 --> 00:25:01,820
He definitely cares about you.

403
00:25:03,540 --> 00:25:04,620
I believe him.

404
00:25:06,020 --> 00:25:08,100
Your Highness, pardon me for talking big.

405
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,780
His Majesty asked me to prepare for this banquet

406
00:25:10,020 --> 00:25:10,860
because he trusted me.

407
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:12,460
No matter what happens,

408
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:14,420
I'll protect you.

409
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:17,100
Chong Lin, thank you.

410
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:18,420
Go and get things ready.

411
00:25:18,860 --> 00:25:19,620
Yes.

412
00:26:16,260 --> 00:26:17,100
How lively!

413
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:20,820
I suppose the banquet has started.

414
00:26:22,340 --> 00:26:23,060
Your Majesty,

415
00:26:24,340 --> 00:26:25,740
where are you?

416
00:26:27,900 --> 00:26:28,660
Jiu'er!

417
00:26:33,260 --> 00:26:33,540
Mother!

418
00:26:33,580 --> 00:26:34,700
Be honest with me.

419
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:36,580
Today is the big day.

420
00:26:36,940 --> 00:26:37,980
Why isn't His Majesty here?

421
00:26:38,260 --> 00:26:38,740
Mother,

422
00:26:39,700 --> 00:26:41,500
His Majesty is delayed by something.

423
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:44,660
Maybe something urgent has happened.

424
00:26:45,540 --> 00:26:47,660
Mother, don't worry.

425
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:50,100
Has he told you where he has gone

426
00:26:50,460 --> 00:26:51,380
and for what?

427
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:53,900
For fear that I might get worried,

428
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:55,140
His Majesty surely wouldn't tell me

429
00:26:55,460 --> 00:26:57,220
these troublesome things.

430
00:26:57,940 --> 00:26:58,780
But mother, look!

431
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,860
His Majesty trusts Chong Lin the most.

432
00:27:01,540 --> 00:27:02,500
He has taken care of

433
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:04,900
the following matters.

434
00:27:05,300 --> 00:27:08,060
He must have received orders from His Majesty.

435
00:27:08,380 --> 00:27:11,100
Mother, no need to worry.

436
00:27:12,340 --> 00:27:12,980
But, Jiu'er...

437
00:27:13,260 --> 00:27:14,020
Mother,

438
00:27:15,820 --> 00:27:17,660
His Majesty is just late.

439
00:27:18,060 --> 00:27:18,980
Moreover,

440
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,820
this is a delayed wedding banquet.

441
00:27:21,220 --> 00:27:22,780
I'm already the Empress of His Majesty.

442
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:25,420
I don't care about these formalities.

443
00:27:31,970 --> 00:27:33,860
I didn't expect Xiaojiu to act so quickly.

444
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:35,340
It's a pity that

445
00:27:35,620 --> 00:27:37,660
I can't drink at her wedding banquet in person.

446
00:27:38,900 --> 00:27:40,300
When it's all over,

447
00:27:40,660 --> 00:27:42,060
you can be a good friend

448
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:43,700
and give her a delayed gift.

449
00:27:43,980 --> 00:27:45,380
Then she'll have a drink with you.

450
00:27:46,460 --> 00:27:47,700
A small gathering between friends

451
00:27:48,420 --> 00:27:50,140
is far better than today's banquet, right?

452
00:27:51,940 --> 00:27:52,700
Right.

453
00:27:52,900 --> 00:27:54,220
Then I'll pick up Ji Heng.

454
00:27:54,460 --> 00:27:55,380
Wherever she wants to go later,

455
00:27:55,380 --> 00:27:56,340
I'll go with her.

456
00:27:56,860 --> 00:27:57,580
What about you?

457
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,340
After all these annoyances are over,

458
00:27:59,500 --> 00:28:00,420
what will you do?

459
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:04,060
After we get rid of Miao Luo,

460
00:28:04,380 --> 00:28:05,620
I still have to handle Nie Chuyin.

461
00:28:06,340 --> 00:28:09,100
The rifts between different races need to be mended.

462
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:11,420
Each race needs a demon lord.

463
00:28:11,780 --> 00:28:13,220
I want to revitalize our clan,

464
00:28:13,540 --> 00:28:14,500
- so I have to pick out more suitable... - So troublesome!

465
00:28:14,780 --> 00:28:15,980
In my opinion,

466
00:28:17,140 --> 00:28:19,140
just kill those traitors directly.

467
00:28:19,460 --> 00:28:20,420
Why do you waste time

468
00:28:20,580 --> 00:28:21,540
talking to them?

469
00:28:25,940 --> 00:28:26,740
Yan,

470
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:29,700
as a demon lord,

471
00:28:29,940 --> 00:28:31,780
the last lesson you need to learn is that

472
00:28:32,700 --> 00:28:35,820
putting away your sword is
for drawing out your sword better.

473
00:28:44,260 --> 00:28:45,740
Your Highness, Emperor Dong Hua is here.

474
00:28:46,020 --> 00:28:47,220
Where is he now?

475
00:28:47,540 --> 00:28:48,260
At the gate of our clan.

476
00:28:48,500 --> 00:28:50,540
Princess Ji Heng is also with him.

477
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:52,100
Ji Heng is back?

478
00:28:52,540 --> 00:28:53,220
Let's go!

479
00:28:54,220 --> 00:28:54,940
You Majesty!

480
00:28:56,980 --> 00:28:57,500
You Majesty!

481
00:28:57,940 --> 00:28:59,700
Emperor Dong Hua is at the camp gate of our clan.

482
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:09,700
Heng'er!

483
00:29:10,220 --> 00:29:11,020
Heng'er!

484
00:29:12,300 --> 00:29:13,220
Ji Heng,

485
00:29:13,380 --> 00:29:15,300
how come the Qiushui Cold Toxin is more severe?

486
00:29:17,060 --> 00:29:18,940
I hate people pestering me endlessly

487
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:20,420
and threatening me with their lives the most.

488
00:29:21,500 --> 00:29:23,260
You're acting so obnoxiously simply

489
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:26,260
because of your father's dragon scale.

490
00:29:29,980 --> 00:29:31,380
Though I've made a promise,

491
00:29:31,860 --> 00:29:34,540
the contents of the promise are for me to decide.

492
00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:36,340
I'll save your life,

493
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:38,380
remove your toxin,

494
00:29:38,620 --> 00:29:40,580
and find you a place within the territory of the demons,

495
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:44,180
thus paying back your father's favor back then.

496
00:29:45,020 --> 00:29:47,460
From now on, the dragon scale will be gone.

497
00:29:48,340 --> 00:29:51,420
In future, whether you're alive or dead,
it'll have nothing to do with me.

498
00:29:51,580 --> 00:29:53,820
I don't want to see you ever again.

499
00:29:56,460 --> 00:29:58,100
Xu Yang, the Demon Lord Chi, I've got an order for you.

500
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,220
Your Majesty!

501
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:05,340
I command you to withdraw your former order

502
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:07,620
and order Demon Princess Ji Heng to return to your land

503
00:30:08,100 --> 00:30:11,340
and never leave this place in future.

504
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:12,780
Any objection?

505
00:30:13,580 --> 00:30:14,100
Your Majesty,

506
00:30:14,660 --> 00:30:16,300
what on earth has Ji Heng done

507
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:16,940
to make you so...

508
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:18,380
Any objection?

509
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,700
No, of course.

510
00:30:37,860 --> 00:30:38,660
Heng'er!

511
00:30:38,980 --> 00:30:39,700
Ji Heng!

512
00:30:40,420 --> 00:30:40,980
Come on.

513
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:42,940
Let's go.

514
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:45,300
Xiaojiu,

515
00:30:46,300 --> 00:30:48,860
how come His Majesty didn't show up

516
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:49,700
at the end of the wedding banquet?

517
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:52,180
What on earth is going on?

518
00:30:54,500 --> 00:30:57,180
His Majesty is delayed by something urgent.

519
00:30:57,500 --> 00:30:58,660
What's so urgent to make him

520
00:30:58,940 --> 00:31:01,180
miss his own wedding banquet?

521
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:03,100
Father,

522
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:05,980
His Majesty really had something urgent to deal with.

523
00:31:07,380 --> 00:31:08,220
What about this?

524
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:10,300
Mother and father, you should go back to Qingqiu first.

525
00:31:10,660 --> 00:31:12,020
When His Majesty returns

526
00:31:12,060 --> 00:31:12,780
after handling his business properly,

527
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:14,660
I'll take him to Qingqiu

528
00:31:14,780 --> 00:31:16,980
and apologize to the elders.

529
00:31:25,180 --> 00:31:26,620
So the so-called urgent business

530
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:29,700
is to leave you behind at the wedding banquet

531
00:31:30,020 --> 00:31:33,020
while messing around with Ji Heng from the demon clan?

532
00:31:33,860 --> 00:31:35,060
Ji Heng?

533
00:31:38,740 --> 00:31:39,300
Right!

534
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:42,460
I know about Ji Heng.

535
00:31:42,740 --> 00:31:44,180
Ji Heng was poisoned with Qiushui Cold Toxin

536
00:31:44,460 --> 00:31:46,700
and has relied on His Majesty
to remove her toxin ever since.

537
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:48,300
His Majesty made a promise

538
00:31:48,500 --> 00:31:49,540
to her father,

539
00:31:49,900 --> 00:31:51,220
so he has pitied her all the time

540
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:52,420
and helped her.

541
00:31:52,820 --> 00:31:53,700
Pity?

542
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:56,140
How come I heard that

543
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:58,180
this morning, he carried Ji Heng

544
00:31:58,700 --> 00:32:01,020
out of the Baishui Mountain majestically

545
00:32:01,300 --> 00:32:02,860
and went directly to the demon clan?

546
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:05,340
I heard that at that time,

547
00:32:05,540 --> 00:32:07,300
the Princess clung to him delicately.

548
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:10,380
It's really hard to tell whether he did that out of pity.

549
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:12,980
A man and a woman

550
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:16,220
stayed at Baishui Mountain last night with no one around.

551
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:18,100
Do you also know that?

552
00:32:19,380 --> 00:32:20,020
Luckily,

553
00:32:20,620 --> 00:32:22,420
now that the demon clan is in a state of siege,

554
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:24,460
it's hard to pass information to both sides.

555
00:32:25,060 --> 00:32:26,460
I suppose only your husband

556
00:32:27,020 --> 00:32:29,700
can make that happen.

557
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:34,020
So only a few know about this.

558
00:32:34,540 --> 00:32:36,580
Otherwise, if immortals from Eight Deserts know about this,

559
00:32:37,140 --> 00:32:40,860
how embarrassed our family will be!

560
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:50,380
Actually, it's not so important if we're embarrassed.

561
00:32:51,180 --> 00:32:54,700
I just can't tolerate that

