00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:59,020
Dong Hua actually betrayed you!

563
00:33:02,820 --> 00:33:05,180
Father! Mother!

564
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:08,100
I want to hear him explain.

565
00:33:09,060 --> 00:33:09,900
Xiaojiu...

566
00:33:13,420 --> 00:33:16,300
Why not go back to Qingqiu with us first?

567
00:33:16,940 --> 00:33:18,260
If Dong Hua really loves you,

568
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:20,420
he'll definitely come to Qingqiu to look for you.

569
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:27,020
Your Highness!

570
00:33:30,300 --> 00:33:32,860
Chong Lin, tell me.

571
00:33:33,060 --> 00:33:34,900
If His Majesty wants to explain to me after coming back,

572
00:33:35,460 --> 00:33:36,780
will two days be enough?

573
00:33:40,300 --> 00:33:41,940
Considering that His Majesty has made no mistake

574
00:33:42,180 --> 00:33:43,940
as the Emperor of the Three Realms,

575
00:33:45,020 --> 00:33:46,180
please don't take Her Highness away.

576
00:33:46,580 --> 00:33:48,020
His Majesty is sure to come back!

577
00:33:51,340 --> 00:33:51,900
Chong Lin,

578
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:55,020
accompany me to the demon land.

579
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:56,900
I want to ask him in person.

580
00:33:57,980 --> 00:33:58,660
Yes.

581
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:49,420
Heng'er!

582
00:34:50,860 --> 00:34:51,740
Your Majesty!

583
00:34:54,140 --> 00:34:56,820
Your Majesty, something's wrong with the blood tear.

584
00:34:57,500 --> 00:35:01,060
Please help us demons!

585
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:02,660
I'll go and investigate myself.

586
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:04,420
Yan!

587
00:35:07,020 --> 00:35:07,660
Heng'er!

588
00:35:08,260 --> 00:35:09,180
Heng'er!

589
00:35:10,700 --> 00:35:12,300
Please go to Bihai Cangling

590
00:35:12,660 --> 00:35:14,300
and explain to Xiaobai in person.

591
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:16,340
After I handle the blood tear,

592
00:35:16,700 --> 00:35:18,380
I'll go back to Bihai Cangling for her.

593
00:35:19,100 --> 00:35:20,420
Do ask her to wait for me.

594
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:24,660
No need to mention everything here to her

595
00:35:24,940 --> 00:35:26,300
in case she gets worried.

596
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:27,420
OK.

597
00:35:41,460 --> 00:35:42,540
Ji Heng, come on.

598
00:35:43,860 --> 00:35:44,380
Xu Yang.

599
00:35:44,380 --> 00:35:45,060
Yan,

600
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:47,260
I've got a secret hiding place.

601
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:50,020
Take Heng'er there and help her settle down.

602
00:35:50,660 --> 00:35:52,380
After we get rid of Miao Luo,

603
00:35:53,140 --> 00:35:54,500
we can take her back.

604
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:57,380
Elder brother!

605
00:35:59,020 --> 00:36:00,300
You're my only sister.

606
00:36:01,220 --> 00:36:02,940
If anything happens to the demons,

607
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:05,020
I have to leave an heiress

608
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:06,940
for our race.

609
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:09,340
Yan,

610
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:11,780
take care of Heng'er for me.

611
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:14,100
OK. I'll be right back.

612
00:36:14,460 --> 00:36:15,860
I'll send Ji Heng to that safe place first

613
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:17,940
and then I'll send the message
to Bihai Cangling for His Majesty.

614
00:36:17,940 --> 00:36:18,900
It'll only take half a day.

615
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:21,380
Stay right beside His Majesty.

616
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:22,500
I see.

617
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:27,540
Be careful!

618
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:29,580
Elder brother!

619
00:36:29,620 --> 00:36:30,260
Go!

620
00:36:33,060 --> 00:36:34,020
Demon Lord!

621
00:36:39,620 --> 00:36:40,300
Demon Lord Xu Yang,

622
00:36:40,620 --> 00:36:42,340
is His Majesty here now?

623
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:43,420
Indeed he is.

624
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:44,660
His Majesty...

625
00:36:46,100 --> 00:36:48,060
Is he with Ji Heng?

626
00:36:49,820 --> 00:36:52,860
His Majesty has taken Ji Heng back to our clan.

627
00:36:53,460 --> 00:36:55,020
Now he has gone to the Forbidden Land

628
00:36:55,340 --> 00:36:57,140
to check the blood tear ward.

629
00:36:58,460 --> 00:36:59,220
Chong Lin.

630
00:36:59,860 --> 00:37:01,620
I won't stay here for long.

631
00:37:02,700 --> 00:37:04,620
Since His Majesty has already been here,

632
00:37:05,500 --> 00:37:06,700
tell him when you see him that

633
00:37:07,100 --> 00:37:08,340
I'll wait for him in Qingqiu.

634
00:37:10,100 --> 00:37:11,100
Your Highness!

635
00:37:14,980 --> 00:37:16,700
Emperor Dong Hua is here.

636
00:37:17,500 --> 00:37:19,460
If you're up to something,

637
00:37:19,700 --> 00:37:21,860
you'd better stop.

638
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:26,300
Incompetent as you are, how can you be a demon lord?

639
00:37:26,700 --> 00:37:29,420
The demons are really declining.

640
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:24,300
Your Majesty,

641
00:38:24,740 --> 00:38:26,380
Demon Lord Xu Yang was killed brutally.

642
00:38:27,940 --> 00:38:29,140
The Miaoyi Chasm!

643
00:38:44,420 --> 00:38:45,260
Slow down.

644
00:38:53,500 --> 00:38:54,100
I've checked around.

645
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:55,860
Xu Yang has protected this place well.

646
00:38:56,220 --> 00:38:57,140
Stay right here.

647
00:38:57,300 --> 00:38:58,220
Wait for me to pick you up.

648
00:38:58,420 --> 00:38:59,780
Except Xu Yang or me, don't trust

649
00:39:00,060 --> 00:39:01,100
anyone who comes to pick you up.

650
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:04,580
Leave me alone.

651
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:06,700
Yan,

652
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:09,940
why are you so good to me?

653
00:39:10,700 --> 00:39:13,220
Haven't you seen what I had done for His Majesty

654
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:16,980
and how he treated me?

655
00:39:18,100 --> 00:39:19,060
The ice face is not the lucky guy.

656
00:39:19,380 --> 00:39:20,380
He doesn't deserve you.

657
00:39:20,660 --> 00:39:22,580
I care about you. It has nothing to do with that.

658
00:39:29,020 --> 00:39:30,980
I actually knelt down

659
00:39:32,100 --> 00:39:36,060
and used my late father to threaten him.

660
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:40,020
I humbled myself to the dust

661
00:39:40,940 --> 00:39:43,620
and became someone I hate.

662
00:39:47,100 --> 00:39:48,300
Why?

663
00:39:49,420 --> 00:39:52,260
How come I've become such a woman?

664
00:39:52,900 --> 00:39:53,900
How come I've become

665
00:39:54,020 --> 00:39:56,060
someone I hate?

666
00:39:58,540 --> 00:40:01,340
Now I'm the disgrace of the demons.

667
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:02,020
Ji Heng,

668
00:40:02,380 --> 00:40:03,380
look at me!

669
00:40:04,540 --> 00:40:05,740
I've loved you for so long

670
00:40:06,140 --> 00:40:07,740
and pursued you for so long.

671
00:40:08,140 --> 00:40:09,460
Do you find me

672
00:40:09,460 --> 00:40:11,300
a humiliating and cowardly demon lord?

673
00:40:14,100 --> 00:40:15,140
You're not!

674
00:40:15,460 --> 00:40:16,260
Right.

675
00:40:16,820 --> 00:40:18,700
You like him and want to be with him,

676
00:40:19,100 --> 00:40:20,460
so you've tried everything to get him.

677
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,460
What's wrong with that?

678
00:40:22,900 --> 00:40:24,340
Yan,

679
00:40:25,380 --> 00:40:27,500
I don't deserve your care.

680
00:40:27,780 --> 00:40:29,860
It's for me to decide whether you deserve it or not.

681
00:40:33,060 --> 00:40:33,660
Ji Heng,

682
00:40:34,100 --> 00:40:35,740
I've got something important to attend to.

683
00:40:36,140 --> 00:40:37,180
As to what I'm gonna say next,

684
00:40:37,340 --> 00:40:39,420
you can take your time and think about it while you're here.

685
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:42,340
I don't care what you and the ice face were

686
00:40:42,700 --> 00:40:44,460
and what you will be.

687
00:40:44,780 --> 00:40:46,100
I only care about you.

688
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:47,700
If you're upset,

689
00:40:47,940 --> 00:40:49,620
I might as well destroy the Sky Kingdom.

690
00:40:51,580 --> 00:40:54,100
I've only loved you in my entire life.

691
00:40:54,540 --> 00:40:55,980
Whenever you turn round,

692
00:40:57,020 --> 00:40:57,860
I'm here.

693
00:41:01,300 --> 00:41:03,500
Even if I remain obsessive,

694
00:41:04,140 --> 00:41:05,940
will you still wait for me?

695
00:41:06,540 --> 00:41:08,020
I've waited for you for tens of thousands of years.

696
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:09,140
Compared to me,

697
00:41:09,380 --> 00:41:11,180
your tiny bit of obsession is nothing.

698
00:41:13,900 --> 00:41:14,780
Do you still remember

699
00:41:15,060 --> 00:41:15,740
the poem you liked to chant

700
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:17,780
under the moon the most?

701
00:41:19,540 --> 00:41:21,220
Green, green the reed,

702
00:41:21,620 --> 00:41:23,180
dew and frost gleam.

703
00:41:23,860 --> 00:41:25,460
Where's she I need?

704
00:41:25,860 --> 00:41:27,340
Beyond the stream.

705
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:30,980
Upstream I go,

706
00:41:31,700 --> 00:41:33,460
The way is long.

707
00:41:34,020 --> 00:41:35,900
Downstream I go,

708
00:41:36,700 --> 00:41:39,620
she's there among.

709
00:41:40,940 --> 00:41:41,660
Tell me.

710
00:41:42,900 --> 00:41:46,380
Will someone also go upstream for me

711
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:49,100
despite the changes of heaven and earth

712
00:41:49,580 --> 00:41:51,540
or the evanescence of worldly affairs?

713
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:55,380
Where's she I need?

714
00:41:56,300 --> 00:41:58,260
Beyond the stream.

715
00:42:02,780 --> 00:42:03,780
You failed to get an answer

716
00:42:03,980 --> 00:42:05,020
from Min Su back then,

717
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:06,420
but now I'll answer you.

718
00:42:07,740 --> 00:42:08,340
Yes.

719
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:09,980
I did it.

720
00:42:11,940 --> 00:42:12,940
The road to follow you

721
00:42:13,220 --> 00:42:14,860
is indeed perilous and endless,

722
00:42:15,620 --> 00:42:17,060
but every time I felt frustrated,

723
00:42:17,460 --> 00:42:19,020
I would remember how you smiled at me

724
00:42:19,100 --> 00:42:20,220
when we first met.

725
00:42:22,180 --> 00:42:23,500
I will definitely protect you

726
00:42:24,140 --> 00:42:25,860
so that you can smile like that all the time.

727
00:42:32,980 --> 00:42:34,460
This place is very safe.

728
00:42:34,940 --> 00:42:37,820
Xu Yang really cares about you.

729
00:42:38,380 --> 00:42:40,100
Feel relieved to heal your wounds here.

730
00:42:40,460 --> 00:42:41,740
When it's all over,

731
00:42:43,540 --> 00:42:44,580
I'll see you again.

732
00:42:47,220 --> 00:42:47,940
Yan,

733
00:42:48,500 --> 00:42:53,900
this time, the demons, my elder brother and you,

734
00:42:53,900 --> 00:42:54,380
will you all...

735
00:42:54,500 --> 00:42:55,220
Don't worry!

736
00:42:57,140 --> 00:42:58,100
Your elder brother and I will be here.

737
00:42:58,380 --> 00:42:59,380
Everything's gonna be all right.

738
00:43:01,580 --> 00:43:02,260
Thank you.

739
00:43:03,180 --> 00:43:04,260
For what?

740
00:43:04,580 --> 00:43:06,380
I said when we first met that

741
00:43:06,620 --> 00:43:08,380
I would die to protect Demon Lord Xu Yang

742
00:43:08,540 --> 00:43:10,020
and Princess Ji Heng.

743
00:43:11,580 --> 00:43:12,460
You'll be fine.

744
00:43:12,820 --> 00:43:13,740
So are the demons.

745
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:15,860
Feel relieved and wait for me to return.

746
00:43:17,780 --> 00:43:18,620
Yan,

747
00:43:19,940 --> 00:43:20,860
promise me

748
00:43:22,420 --> 00:43:24,140
to return safely, OK?

749
00:43:33,460 --> 00:43:34,780
I'll wait for you to return!

